*Rate of twist: 406 mm
*Rifling: 6 left-hand twist
*Capacity: 7+1 rounds (7 in standard-capacity magazine +1 in firing chamber)
*Muzzle velocity: 253m/s
*Muzzle energy: 477J
*Rate of fire: 35 rounds/min (practical)
*Caliber: .45 (11.43mm)
*Effective range: 50m
*Overall length: 160mm
*Height: 133 mm
*Length: 210 mm

