== M1911 Trivia ==
===Character settings===
M1911 is the first gun for every players, but other then that, due to the high drop rate and not so effective buffs, she was used as food for other T-dolls {{Spoiler| At least her fame is also special.}}

Showed in the second map (night battle) as commander.

Most of the time she was being compared with M9{{Spoiler|Fighting over Commander's :)}} as competitor，causing confusion and sadness.

